    <div class="text-xl py-1">Hello, world!</div>
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">I'm Linh Le (knyL)</h1>
    <div class="text-3xl py-3 font-bold">Software Engineer</div>
    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-md">
        <p>
          My job is to create software that solves problems in a simple way, and
          here's where I share what I learn along the way. The blog is all about
          .NET Core and other related technologies.
          <br />
          I hope you'll gain some knowledge from this blog. See y'all around ðŸ‘‹
        </p>
      </text>
    </div>
